queries.sql: select kode_fakultas from prodi where kode_prodi ='62201' group by kode_prodi

SELECT mk_klaim_dekan.idklaim, mk_klaim_asessor.ta_akademik, mk_klaim_asessor.no_peserta, bio_peserta.nama, mk_klaim_asessor.kode_matakuliah, mk_klaim_asessor.nilai, matakuliah.nama_matakuliah, mk_klaim_asessor.kode_prodi, bio_peserta.jenis_rpl, bio_peserta.instansi_asal, bio_peserta.didikakhir, prodi.nama_prodi, prodi.id_jenjang, fakultas.nama_fakultas, fakultas.kode_fakultas, (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM mk_klaim_asessor as it WHERE mid(it.idklaim,6,10) = mid(mk_klaim_asessor.idklaim,6,10) and it.nilai !='E') as jbaris FROM mk_klaim_dekan LEFT JOIN mk_klaim_asessor ON mk_klaim_dekan.idklaim = mk_klaim_asessor.idklaim LEFT JOIN bio_peserta ON mid(mk_klaim_dekan.idklaim,6,10)= bio_peserta.no_peserta LEFT JOIN matakuliah ON mk_klaim_asessor.kode_matakuliah = matakuliah.kode_matakuliah AND mk_klaim_asessor.kode_prodi = matakuliah.kode_prodi LEFT JOIN prodi ON mk_klaim_asessor.kode_prodi = prodi.kode_prodi LEFT JOIN fakultas ON prodi.kode_fakultas = fakultas.kode_fakultas where mk_klaim_asessor.kode_prodi='62201' and mk_klaim_asessor.idklaim is not null and mk_klaim_asessor.ta_akademik ='20232' and mk_klaim_asessor.nilai != 'E' order by mk_klaim_dekan.idklaim
select dekan from fakultas where kode_fakultas ='60001'
